model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder

Class JumpPointSearchPathFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder.PathFinder
      • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder.JumpPointSearchPathFinder

  • public class JumpPointSearchPathFinder
extends PathFinder
    The jump point search path finder uses jump point search to determine paths. Adapted from: https://github.com/qiao/PathFinding.js/ Original paper: Online Graph Pruning for Pathfinding on Grid Maps, by Daniel Harabor and Alban Grastien.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
